text: Life Left to Go is an album by alternative rock band SafetySuit. It was released in the summer of 2008. The album contains the tracks Someone Like You (SafetySuit song), Stay, and Anywhere But Here. == Track listing == # "Someone Like You" # "Apology" # "Find the Way" # "Stay (SafetySuit song)" # "Something I Said" # "Anywhere But Here" # "Down" # "The Moment" # "Annie" # "What If" # "Gone Away" # "A Life Left to Go" ==Related pages== * SafetySuit Category:2008 albums
title: Life Left to Go
